<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Pawned</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body style="padding-top: 60px">

  <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-inner">
        <div class="container">
          <%= link_to "Pawned", root_path, class: "brand" %>
          <% if player_signed_in? %>
            <div class="navbar-btn btn-group pull-right">
              <%= link_to(admin_player_path(current_player.id), class: "btn btn-primary") do %>
                <%= current_player.name %>
              <% end %>
              <a class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#"><span class="caret"></span></a>
              <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                <li>
                <%= link_to(edit_admin_player_path(current_player.id)) do %>
                  <i class="icon-pencil"></i>
                  Edit
                <% end %>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#"><i class="icon-trash"></i> Some Option</a></li>
                <li><a href="#"><i class="icon-ban-circle"></i> Other Option</a></li>
                <li class="divider"></li>
                <li>
                <%= link_to(destroy_player_session_path, method: :delete) do %>
                  <i class="icon-off"></i>
                  Logout
                <% end %>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <div class="container">
    <% if player_signed_in? %>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span3">
        <h2>Here could be your calendar</h2>
        <p>Next level biodiesel sartorial, keffiyeh selvage synth shoreditch yr pitchfork mixtape fap cardigan lo-fi hoodie. Sriracha wes anderson terry richardson sustainable, jean shorts pour-over mlkshk wolf occupy. Beard small batch farm-to-table aesthetic. Wayfarers synth high life seitan irony. Portland lo-fi brunch, shoreditch bespoke letterpress cardigan. Hoodie squid fixie food truck. Retro quinoa readymade trust fund, mlkshk banh mi vegan.</p>
        <script charset="utf-8" src="http://widgets.twimg.com/j/2/widget.js"></script>
        <script>
        new TWTR.Widget({
          version: 2,
          type: 'search',
          search: 'chess',
          rpp: 10,
          interval: 5000,
          title: 'Some of the world\'s',
          subject: 'Chess Titans',
          width: 'auto',
          height: 300,
          theme: {
            shell: {
              background: '#0074cc',
              color: '#ffffff'
            },
            tweets: {
              background: '#ffffff',
              color: '#444444',
              links: '#0088cc'
            }
          },
          features: {
            scrollbar: false,
            loop: true,
            live: true,
            behavior: 'default'
          }
        }).render().start();
        </script>
      </div>

      <div class="span9">
          <%= yield %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% else %>
      <%= yield %>
    <% end %>

    <hr>

    <footer>
      &copy; Pawnage Software 2012
      <!-- Social icons by: http://www.elegantthemes.com/blog/resources/free-social-media-icon-set -->
      <a><img src="img/facebook.png" class="pull-right" /></a>
      <a><img src="img/twitter.png" class="pull-right" /></a>
      <a><img src="img/google.png" class="pull-right" /></a>
    </footer>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
